--- !u!114 &439223547
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 439223545}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: bb1ca8a195262d1468f9b44c27c9ec55, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CultistsDefeatedDialogue
  cultistEncounterId: CultistScene_Cultists_01
  dialogueTypewriter: {fileID: 242870887}
  defeatedDialogue:
  - speakerName: Paladin
    dialogueText: I owe you an explanation. I am the current leader of the holy knights
      from the city of Seraphion.
    portrait: {fileID: 4907242074090915066, guid: 0fc49aca0aa58be459d3df532d47cdfa, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Kael
    dialogueText: W-what...
    portrait: {fileID: 8859943044834607501, guid: 5740df5ceb0432741999c0000f641d68, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Paladin
    dialogueText: 'Yes, and I am fighting a cult that destroyed your village called
      the Hollow Choir. '
    portrait: {fileID: 4907242074090915066, guid: 0fc49aca0aa58be459d3df532d47cdfa, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Paladin
    dialogueText: Your father used to be the leader of the holy knights in the city
      of Seraphion.
    portrait: {fileID: 4907242074090915066, guid: 0fc49aca0aa58be459d3df532d47cdfa, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Kael
    dialogueText: (That's where Mira goes to school! That also explains a lot...)
    portrait: {fileID: 8859943044834607501, guid: 5740df5ceb0432741999c0000f641d68, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Kael
    dialogueText: So... what happened to everyone? Are they all dead or can we still
      save them?
    portrait: {fileID: 4237676072881026496, guid: 454d1fec3dbc81d4d844ac949f7fb6b6, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Paladin
    dialogueText: It's highly likely your family was taken as sacrifices. They're
      alive, but not for long...
    portrait: {fileID: 4907242074090915066, guid: 0fc49aca0aa58be459d3df532d47cdfa, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Kael
    dialogueText: Then lets hurry! I need that potion up ahead for my talented mage
      friend Mira.
    portrait: {fileID: 4907242074090915066, guid: 0fc49aca0aa58be459d3df532d47cdfa, type: 3}
  dialogueDelay: 0.1
  disablePlayerMovementDuringDialogue: 0
